On Escalation Ticket # 00433693 the new comment has been added: Iuri Tovcaci:

@WaitingOnEngineer , 

Please use the following link to download a test build with Windows native OCR (which should have better performance):
https://download.endpointprotector.com/custom_agent/Epp29012025/EPPClient_v6.2.4.0054.zip

Additionally, you might want to test with DPI disabled for Outlook (on the "Deep Packet Inspection" server settings page) and with the add-in enabled.

Would you still like the customer to test with the build with Outlook removed from advanced system scanning?
